dPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5 Important Factors to Help You Choose the Best Contact Form Plugin for WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As vital as contact forms are to the success of your online business, WordPress doesn&#8217;t come with a built-in contact form. To build a contact form for your website, you&#8217;ll need to install a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"WordPress plugin\">WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, despite the thousands of contact form plugins on the market, they aren&#8217;t all built the same. Each has its strengths and weaknesses, while many are downright inefficient.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why you must be careful when choosing the contact form plugin for your WordPress website. Here are a few things to look out for as you shop around for the best contact form for WordPress:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the first things to look for in a contact form plugin is the features. The best WordPress contact form plugins enable you to create any kind of online form that helps you grow your business. This includes contact forms, payment forms, user registration forms, and any type of form you need.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ease of Use&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Particularly if you like taking a DIY approach to your online business, you&#8217;ll want to focus on contact form plugins that offer exceptional ease of use. These make creating forms easy and come with an intuitive user interface. Generally speaking, the shorter the learning curve, the better.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Responsiveness</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Research shows that mobile devices drive as much as <a href=\"https://www.perficient.com/insights/research-hub/mobile-vs-desktop-usage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"61% of website traffic in the US\">61% of website traffic in the US</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why your contact forms must be 100% responsive. They should look and work great on all devices. Otherwise, you could lose a lot of leads.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pricing</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Like all business tools, a contact form plugin is an investment. Therefore, you must ensure that your choice gives you great value for money.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Documentation and Support</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another crucial factor to consider as you shop around for the best contact form plugins for WordPress is documentation. The plugin&#8217;s documentation should be detailed and easy to understand. Then, walking through the features, installation and use should be a breeze.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides documentation, you&#8217;ll also want to ensure your contact form plugin of choice is developed by a team with a good reputation for good customer support.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what to look for in the best contact form plugin for WordPress, let&#8217;s get right to our top five.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5 Best Contact Form Plugins for WordPress You Should Consider</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember, a contact form is essential to building your online audience. As such, you need to get the best contact form plugin for your website. Let&#8217;s quickly jump to our top recommendations, shall we?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"WPForms\">WPForms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for the best contact form plugin for WordPress, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"WPForms\">WPForms</a> is undoubtedly it.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"341\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-wpforms.png\" alt=\"If you\'re looking for the best contact form plugin for WordPress, WPForms is probably it.\" class=\"wp-image-68620\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-wpforms.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-wpforms-300x146.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-wpforms-600x292.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many reasons WPForms ranks as the best contact form plugin for WordPress. For one, it&#8217;s one of the most user-friendly contact form plugins on the market. Whether you&#8217;re a techie or have little technical knowledge, you&#8217;ll find WPForms super-easy to use.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason WPForms is an excellent option is that it offers exceptional flexibility. You can use it to create any kind of form you want. Besides this, you can also easily edit your forms in real-time right from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One factor that sets WPForms apart is the ability to create <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/introducing-conversational-forms-by-wpforms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"conversational forms\">conversational forms</a>. This feature helps boost conversion rates. Other features you can expect from this powerful contact form plugin include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Massive template library</li><li>Automatic email notifications when people fill in your forms</li><li>Vast customization options</li><li>Integrates easily with most email marketing services and CRMs</li><li>Captures emails even when people don&#8217;t finish filling out forms</li><li>Comes with a surveys and polls addon&nbsp;</li><li>Robust security</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms allows you to build beautiful user-focused contact forms. But, more than that, it&#8217;s a tool that helps you run optimized lead generation campaigns.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you&#8217;re looking for the best contact form plugin for WordPress, WPForms comes highly recommended.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can get started with WPForms for free. However, if you feel you need to upgrade, you&#8217;ll be glad to know paid plans start at a mere $31.60/year (you save over $47).</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Formidable Forms\">Formidable Forms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Need a contact form plugin that comes with many bells and whistles?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Formidable Forms\">Formidable Forms</a> could be what you&#8217;re looking for.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"354\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-formidable-forms.png\" alt=\"Formidable Forms ranks as one of the brest contact form plugins for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-68623\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-formidable-forms.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-formidable-forms-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-formidable-forms-600x303.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Formidable Forms is a powerful all-in-one WordPress form builder with powerful addons. These help you create any type of contact form you want, from simple contact forms to more complex multiple-page forms.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Power users will love the Formidable Views feature. It allows users to format, filter, and display user-submitted data right on the website&#8217;s front-end.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some features that help make it a breeze to create contact forms with Formidable Forms include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Drag and drop form builder for ease of use</li><li>Powerful no-code customization options</li><li>Create advanced forms using features like conditional logic</li><li>Spam protection</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>No matter the kind of form you want to create, Formidable Form&#8217;s user-friendly interface can help you easily create one.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The only drawback with Formidable Forms is it&#8217;s not as intuitive as WPForms. The reason is that it was mainly developed for advanced users. However, if building beautiful conversion-focused forms is a priority, then Formidable Forms should be on your list of the best contact form plugins for WordPress.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for pricing, Formidable Forms comes with several paid plans starting at $39.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ninja-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ninja Forms\">Ninja Forms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When searching for the best contact form plugin for WordPress, you&#8217;ll undoubtedly come across <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ninja-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ninja Forms\">Ninja Forms</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ninja-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"298\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-ninja-forms.png\" alt=\"Ninja Forms is another contender for the best contact form plugin for WordPress award.\" class=\"wp-image-68629\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-ninja-forms.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-ninja-forms-300x128.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-ninja-forms-600x255.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ninja Forms is so popular because it&#8217;s super easy to use. With a simple interface and an intuitive drag-and-drop contact form builder, you can use it to easily build beautiful-looking contact forms. Like WPForms, you can do this even if you&#8217;re not tech-savvy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another advantage of Ninja Forms is that you can get started with the base version of the plugin for free. After that, you&#8217;ll have to buy addons to extend its functionality. However, if you need more than two addons, the price will surpass WPForms. So, if you need a contact form plugin that&#8217;s flexible and offers you more functionality, WPForms offers more value for money.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Features to expect from Ninja Forms include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Developer-friendly options for advanced users</li><li><span>Highly customizable</span></li><li>Easily manage and export form submissions</li><li>Extend the functionality with over 40 premium addons</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Ninja Forms also makes it easy to run your marketing campaigns as it integrates seamlessly with other marketing tools like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"MailChimp\">MailChimp</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Constant Contact\">Constant Contact</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hubspot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Hubspot\">Hubspot</a>, and more.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing for Ninja Forms starts at $29/year for the lowest plan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hubspot-wordpress-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Hubspot Forms\">Hubspot Forms</a> </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While not a standalone form builder, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hubspot-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"Hubspot\'s WordPress plugin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Hubspot&#8217;s WordPress plugin</a> is an excellent all-in-one marketing plugin. One of its most useful features in the form builder.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/hubspot-wordpress-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"335\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-hubspot.png\" alt=\"Hubspot\'s WordPress plugin isv another plugin that fits the bill of best contact form plugin for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-68634\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-hubspot.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-hubspot-300x144.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-hubspot-600x287.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of being an all-in-one marketing plugin, Hubspot has the advantage of making it easy to collect customer data, segment it, and run outreach campaigns — all from a single dashboard. A few noteworthy features of Hubspot include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Intuitive drag and drop form builder</li><li>Create forms from scratch or customize ready-made templates</li><li>Over 1,000 form fields and dozens of field types to choose from</li><li>Automatic form submission notifications&nbsp;</li><li>Over 850 integrations are available in the HubSpot ecosystem and beyond</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re already using some of Hubspot&#8217;s other tools, then this plugin could be a no-brainer. However, if you prefer ease-of-use or greater flexibility, WPForms also integrates well with Hubspot.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/gravityforms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Gravity Forms\">Gravity Forms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to premium contact form plugins, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/gravityforms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Gravity Forms\">Gravity Forms</a> ranks among the best.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/gravityforms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"286\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-gravity-forms.png\" alt=\"Gravity Forms is another excellent option if you\'re looking for the best contact form plugin for WordPress. \" class=\"wp-image-68637\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-gravity-forms.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-gravity-forms-300x123.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-gravity-forms-600x245.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Gravity Forms comes with powerful features designed for both novice and advanced users. Besides the intuitive drag-and-drop form builder, Gravity Forms comes with other features such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Workflow automation</li><li>Conditional logic</li><li>Secure data collection</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Because Gravity Forms doesn&#8217;t have a free plan, it can be an expensive option for small businesses. However, if you run multiple sites, the cost will even out. FYI, plans start at $59/year for a single site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Best Contact Form Plugin for WordPress to Avoid: Contact Form 7</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/contact-form-7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Contact Form 7\">Contact Form 7</a> is one of the oldest and most downloaded contact form plugins in the WordPress ecosystem. However, we don&#8217;t recommend it.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/contact-form-7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"195\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7.png\" alt=\"When looking for the best contact form plugin for WordPress, avoid Contact Form 7.\" class=\"wp-image-68643\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7-300x98.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One mistake many users of this plugin make is relying on the download numbers. Since it&#8217;s been downloaded millions of times, then it&#8217;s a good plugin, right?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not really.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The main reason Contact Form 7 is downloaded a lot is that it&#8217;s free. It&#8217;s also downloaded a lot because of herd mentality — people opt for it because it has a high active install.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, Contact Form 7 has more cons than pros. For example, the user interface is not intuitive, making it difficult for beginners to make beautiful contact forms. Also, because it&#8217;s free, support is very limited. Here are some recent reviews from some users:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"587\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7-2.png\" alt=\"Contact Form 7 is rated as one of the best contact form plugins for WordPress, but recent reviews say otherwise.\" class=\"wp-image-68839\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7-2-300x252.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-contact-form-plugin-for-wordpress-contact-form-7-2-600x503.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>So, as you look for the best free contact form plugin for WordPress, avoid Contact Form 7. Instead, opt for better options like WPForms Lite.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While Contact Form 7 is touted as one of the best free contact form plugins for WordPress, there are better options.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Which is the Best Contact Form Plugin for WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the best contact form plugin for WordPress between these five is still a daunting task.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, which should you choose from the list above?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, if you&#8217;re looking for ease of use and powerful flexibility, we recommend <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"WPForms\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If, however, you&#8217;re tech-savvy and want to build more complex forms, then <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Formidable Forms\">Formidable Forms</a> would be the best contact form plugin for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Contact Form Plugin for WordPress — Boost Your Conversions with SEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For your target audience to find your contact form and fill it, you need to have an excellent search engine optimization (SEO) strategy in place. To power your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-hacks-to-grow-your-traffic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"SEO strategy\">SEO strategy