;s:495:\"<p>Need a powerful headline analyzer tool to help you craft scroll-stopping headlines? It’s easy to overlook the importance of headlines when creating online content. Despite being a relatively small element, headlines play a huge role in search engine optimization (SEO).&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-headline-analyzer-tool/\">7 Best WordPress Headline Analyzer Tools for Writing Better Headlines</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16413:\"<p>Need a powerful headline analyzer tool to help you craft scroll-stopping headlines?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s easy to overlook the importance of headlines when creating online content. Despite being a relatively small element, headlines play a huge role in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">search engine optimization</a> (SEO). They are also vital in proving search intent to users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, SEO is not just about <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">keyword analysis</a> or <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">meta descriptions</a>. It also involves many other aspects. One such is crafting optimized headlines. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why getting your headline just right is essential to driving relevant traffic to your website. It also helps improve your conversion rate if your post fulfills the promise in the headline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But crafting a compelling headline is no easy task.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It requires you to come up with different iterations. When you succeed in crafting a couple of good ones, knowing which works best is still not easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A headline analyzer tool makes the entire headline writing process much easier.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Without further ado, let’s quickly look at the seven best WordPress headline analyzer tools you can use to create eye-catching headlines.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. AIOSEO&nbsp; Headline Analyzer Tool</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Not to toot our own horn, but we put in a lot of love into creating the AIOSEO headline analyzer tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"283\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-headline-analyzer-tool-AIOSEO.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO has the best WordPress headline nalyzer tool on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-65771\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-headline-analyzer-tool-AIOSEO.png 283w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-headline-analyzer-tool-AIOSEO-142x300.png 142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO’s headline analyzer is one of the best on the market. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-headline-analyzer-in-all-in-one-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">It’s easy to use</a> and has a clean, intuitive user interface that makes it easy to understand the headline recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"297\" height=\"598\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-aioseo-1.png\" alt=\"A good headline analyzer tool gives good recommendations on improving your headline.\" class=\"wp-image-65354\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-aioseo-1.png 297w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-aioseo-1-149x300.png 149w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best features of the AIOSEO headline analyzer tool is that you get feedback on your headline right within WordPress and in real-time. The tool analyzes elements such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Power words</li><li>Common words</li><li>Uncommon words</li><li>Emotional words</li><li>Sentiment</li><li>Headline type</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>After analyzing the various elements, the headline analyzer will give you a score for your headline. It will also offer recommendations on how to improve your headline.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another advantage of the AIOSEO headline analyzer is that it measures the character length of your headline. Doing so helps ensure your headline doesn’t get truncated on search engine results pages (SERPs). As a result, you’ll enjoy better click-through rates as users will know exactly what your post is about.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO’s headline analyzer comes free with the AIOSEO plugin.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IsItWP Headline Analyzer Tool</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another excellent WordPress headline analyzer tool you should consider is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IsItWP headline analyzer</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"984\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-isitwp.png\" alt=\"IsItWP is a fantastic headline analyzer tool you should consider adding to your tool set.\" class=\"wp-image-65355\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-isitwp.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-isitwp-213x300.png 213w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-isitwp-600x843.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being free, the IsItWP headline analyzer tool also has other great features to write home about. For example, it’s one of the easiest to use. All you have to do is plug in your headline and click analyze. The tool will then grade your headline and give you valuable information to help you create better headlines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>IsItWP also features a headline writing tutorial underneath the headline results. This can come in quite handy if you need ideas on how to improve your headline.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Headline Analyzer Tool by OptinMonster</a> </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>OptinMonster is a well-known name in the world of conversion optimization. So it’s no wonder that the <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">OptinMonster headline analyzer</a> is one of the best on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"619\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-optinmonster-619x1024.png\" alt=\"Another excellent headline analyzer tool to consider is OptinMonster.\" class=\"wp-image-65356\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-optinmonster-619x1024.png 619w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-optinmonster-181x300.png 181w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-optinmonster-600x993.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-optinmonster.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 619px) 100vw, 619px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>OptinMonster’s headline analyzer tool is super-easy to use. It also has a handy feature that shows essential elements of effective headlines. For example, it helps with emotional words that help readers connect to your headline. It also shows you the power words in your headline that help boost conversions. If you’re lacking on the power words front, check out OptinMonster’s fantastic post on <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/700-power-words-that-will-boost-your-conversions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">power words</a>.  </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. <a href=\"https://coschedule.com/headline-analyzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Headline Studio by CoSchedule</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Formerly known as the CoSchedule Headline Analyzer, <a href=\"https://coschedule.com/headline-analyzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Headline Studio</a> is another great tool you can use to create perfect headlines.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://coschedule.com/headline-analyzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"327\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-coschedule.png\" alt=\"CoSchedule\'s Headline Studio is a great headline analyzer you should consider.\" class=\"wp-image-65357\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-coschedule.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-coschedule-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-coschedule-600x280.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Being one of the oldest headline analyzer tools on the market, Headline Studio has some unique features other headline analyzers miss. A great example is the revision history feature. This feature helps you keep track of the tweaks you make to your headline so you can fall back on the best one if subsequent iterations are missing the mark. It also comes with a thesaurus and a word bank to help you quickly make changes to your headline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll have to create an account first before accessing your Headline report. However, this is worth the extra effort as all your headlines are saved, and you can access them via your account.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The only downside to Headline Studio is that most advanced features are only available on the paid plan, which starts at $9/month.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <a href=\"https://www.aminstitute.com/headline/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Emotional Marketing Value Headline Analyzer</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another veteran in the headline analyzer tool space is the <a href=\"https://www.aminstitute.com/headline/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Emotional Marketing Value Headline Analyzer</a> by the Advanced Marketing Institute.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://www.aminstitute.com/headline/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"975\" height=\"612\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-emv-headline-analyzer.png\" alt=\"The EMV headline analyzer is a headline analyzer tool that focuses on the emotions headlines elicit.\" class=\"wp-image-65358\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-emv-headline-analyzer.png 975w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-emv-headline-analyzer-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-emv-headline-analyzer-768x482.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-emv-headline-analyzer-600x377.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The Advanced Marketing Institute developed this tool to help you gauge the percentage of emotional marketing value (EMV) words in your headline. These are words that are likely to have an emotional impact on readers. The tool then gives you a score out of 100.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides giving you a score, the EMV headline analyzer also highlights which type of emotion your headlines impact the most. It breaks them into three categories: intellectual, empathetic, and spiritual. This will help you craft headlines that appeal to the emotions you&#8217;re trying to elicit in your readers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>6. <a href=\"https://headlines.sharethrough.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Sharethrough Headline Analyzer</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another headline analyzer tool to have on your radar is <a href=\"https://headlines.sharethrough.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Sharethrough</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://headlines.sharethrough.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"982\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-sharethrough.png\" alt=\"Sharethrough\'s headline analyzer tool has fast grown in popularity thanks to it\'s clean interface and helpful feedback.\" class=\"wp-image-65361\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-sharethrough.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-sharethrough-214x300.png 214w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-sharethrough-600x842.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One notable feature of the tool is that it gives you insight into the strengths and weaknesses of your headline. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This makes it easier for you to create better iterations of your headline. Besides the headline score, Sharethrough also gives you two other scores for your headline:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Engagement score</li><li>Impression score</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These are designed to help you further optimize your headline.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>7. <a href=\"https://capitalizemytitle.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Capitalize My Title Headline Analyzer</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://capitalizemytitle.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Capitalize My Title</a> headline analyzer tool is the last tool on our list of the best WordPress headline analyzers.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://capitalizemytitle.com/headline-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"429\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-capitalize-my-title.png\" alt=\"Capitalize My Title is a headline analyzer tool that features on many best headline analyzer tool lists. \" class=\"wp-image-65362\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-capitalize-my-title.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-capitalize-my-title-300x184.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/headline-analyzer-tool-capitalize-my-title-600x368.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Capitalize My Title is a great headline analyzer that gives you an easy-to-understand score for your headline. It goes a step further by also showing the sentiment behind your headline and the readability of your headline. It also gives some suggestions on how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-change-the-seo-title-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">improve your headline for SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, great as it is, it has one big drawback — it comes with many ads. These can distract from the overall experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best WordPress Headline Analyzer Tool — Powering Your Headlines for Success</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Headline analyzers are great tools for helping ensure that your content performs well. After all, poorly crafted headlines result in your content being ignored, no matter how good it is.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, optimizing your headlines for search engines and people leads to greater visibility and increased traffic. It also results in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">higher click-through rates</a> and, ultimately, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/5-reasons-why-your-website-is-not-converting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">conversions</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, yes. Headlines are important. That’s why you must leverage a headline analyzer tool to ensure that yours is optimized.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Which headline analyzer do we recommend?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ll have to go with AIOSEO’s headline analyzer tool for several reasons. For one, it’s free. But the most significant factor is that it works right within WordPress. This ensures that you can easily optimize all your blog post’s elements from one place.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go ahead and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">download the AIOSEO plugin now</a> and optimize your headlines and entire site as well.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-headline-analyzer-tool/\">7 Best WordPress Headline Analyzer Tools for Writing Better Headlines</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellform