:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Membership sites\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"WordPress membership plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=65138\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:466:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Membership plugin for WordPress? With so many promising you the moon, finding one that actually does what it claims can be daunting. That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve hand-picked seven membership plugins that you should consider as&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-membership-plugin-for-wordpress/\">The Best Membership Plugin for WordPress (Top 7 Compared)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21324:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Membership plugin for WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many promising you the moon, finding one that actually does what it claims can be daunting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve hand-picked seven membership plugins that you should consider as you <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/create-a-membership-site-with-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">build your membership site</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a WordPress Membership Site?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A WordPress membership site is a website built on WordPress. It&#8217;s structured so that users can only access certain areas or content after paying. For example, you can restrict access to (among other things):</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Content</li><li>Downloads</li><li>Forums</li><li>Courses&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason users prefer WordPress is the way it&#8217;s easy to use . It&#8217;s also flexible and offers a lot of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">search engine optimization</a> (SEO) options. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Membership sites are fast becoming popular. This is because people are social creatures that need to belong to a group of like-minded peers. It&#8217;s because of this that they have become an excellent way to make money online.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fortunately, you don&#8217;t need to pay a developer loads of cash to build yours. All you need is a membership plugin that will enable you to create various membership access levels and allow you to receive payments from users.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What to Look for in the Best Membership Plugin for WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides membership levels and payment gateway integration, there&#8217;s a lot involved in setting up your membership site just the way you want it to run. That&#8217;s why you must be meticulous about checking out each plugin&#8217;s functionality. Some features to look out for in a membership plugin include:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features and Flexibility</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Membership plugins come in many different flavors. You can get lightweight and fast plugins that have limited features. On the opposite end of the spectrum, you can get full-feature plugins. These give you the flexibility to create a membership site tailored to your exact needs. Of course, you can also get something in-between.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Compatibility&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another factor to consider as you shop around for the best membership plugin for WordPress is compatibility. First, check whether your preferred plugin works well with other website elements. For example, does it integrate well with your theme and other plugins? To do this, you can try out your plugin on a staging site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ease of Use</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you intend to be hands-on with the development and maintenance of your membership site? </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then ease of use must be a deciding factor when choosing a membership plugin. This means your plugin of choice should have an intuitive dashboard. It must also make it easy to integrate essential add-ons like payment gateways.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that being said, let&#8217;s dive right into the seven best membership plugins for WordPress sites.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Top 7 Best Membership Plugin for WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Contrary to popular belief, you don&#8217;t need to pay truckloads of money to build a membership site. All you need is a powerful plugin that will help you transform your basic website into a thriving community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that said, let&#8217;s quickly look at seven of the best membership plugins for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/memberpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MemberPress</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to WordPress membership plugins, none are as celebrated as <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/memberpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MemberPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/memberpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"331\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-memberpress.png\" alt=\"MemberPress is one of the best membership plugins for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-65139\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-memberpress.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-memberpress-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-memberpress-600x284.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>MemberPress is a powerful WordPress plugin that can help transform your website into a membership site. Besides being super-easy to use, it also comes with a robust feature set that allows you to build any membership site you want.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best features of MemberPress is that it gives you the flexibility to create an unlimited number of memberships. You can also customize membership levels, including the price for each level, access to content at each level, and much more. You&#8217;ll also love MemberPress&#8217;s easy integration with plugins like <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/bbpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">bbPress</a>. These are excellent for building communities and forums. Other great features you&#8217;ll love with MemberPress include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Integrates with popular email service providers (ESPs).</li><li>LMS add-on that enables you to build and sell courses easily.</li><li>Powerful access rules that enable content restriction at various levels.</li><li>Easy-to-set up content dripping and contact access expiration.</li><li>Easy Affiliate integration makes it easy to create your own affiliate program.</li><li>Sell digital and physical products.</li><li>Customizable checkout page.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the drawbacks of MemberPress is that the payment gateways are limited. Other than that, you can rest assured your membership site will be built using one of the best plugins around. Also, when it comes to features, MemberPress is almost unbeatable.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for price, MemberPress pricing starts at $179/year for one site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/restrict-content-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Restrict Content Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a lightweight membership plugin that still affords you the ability to create powerful membership sites?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/restrict-content-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Restrict Content Pro</a> is the answer.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/restrict-content-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"581\" height=\"552\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-restrict-content-pro.png\" alt=\"One of the best membership plugins for WordPress is Restricted Content Pro.\" class=\"wp-image-65140\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-restrict-content-pro.png 581w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-restrict-content-pro-300x285.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 581px) 100vw, 581px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Particularly if you&#8217;re new to membership sites, you&#8217;ll find Restrict Content Pro to be a godsend. This is thanks to its ease of use and the ultra-clear user documentation. Coming from the same stable as popular plugins like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-woocommerce-seo-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">AffiliateWP</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-woocommerce-seo-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Easy Digital Downloads</a>, you can expect nothing but the best from this WordPress membership plugin. Notable features to expect include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Different membership levels</li><li>Intuitive customer dashboard (for members)</li><li>Content dripping</li><li>Create unlimited subscription packages</li><li>Payment integrations with Stripe, Braintree, 2Checkout, and PayPal</li><li>WooCommerce integration</li><li>Prorated memberships</li><li>Data and analytics dashboard</li><li>Easily offer discounts or create coupons on membership subscriptions</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Another good things is that developers constantly adding new features to the plugin. As a result, Restrict Content Pro is fast growing into a plugin that fits the bill of best membership plugin for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite pricing starting at only $99/year, Restrict Content Pro comes chock full of features that make it easy to create and run memberships sites.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce-memberships/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WooCommerce Memberships</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another plugin you should consider as you shop around for the best membership plugin for WordPress is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce-memberships/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WooCommerce Memberships</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce-memberships/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"357\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-woocommerce-memberships.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Memberships is highly rated as one of the best membership plugins for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-65141\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-woocommerce-memberships.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-woocommerce-memberships-300x153.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-woocommerce-memberships-600x306.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have an online store built using WooCommerce, consider adding another revenue stream by selling subscriptions. The WooCommerce Membership plugin can help you easily do this. By integrating membership perks with your store, you can encourage purchases and subscriptions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With WooCommerce Memberships, you can set up subscriptions for recurring or one-time payments. However, if you&#8217;re to accept recurring payments, you&#8217;ll also need the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce-subscriptions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WooCommerce Subscriptions</a> plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What features can you expect from WooCommerce Memberships?</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Invite-only members area</li><li>Drip content&nbsp;</li><li>Option to offer free shipping for members</li><li>Easy communication with members via &#8220;Membership Notes.&#8221;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A huge advantage of WooCommerce Memberships is that you can leverage <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-woocommerce-seo-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WooCommerce SEO plugins</a> to help boost your visibility and thus grow your membership site. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>WooCommerce Memberships comes with one pricing plan that will set you back $199/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">LearnDash </a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For those in the business of creating and selling online courses, one of the best WordPress membership plugins in the industry is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/learndash/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">LearnDash</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/learndash/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"270\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-learndash.png\" alt=\"For those in the online course niche, LearnDash is the best membership plugin for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-65142\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-learndash.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-learndash-300x116.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-learndash-600x231.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>LearnDash is an excellent WordPress LMS plugin that&#8217;s easy to use. It also offers exceptional flexibility for creating membership plans of your choice.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One thing you&#8217;ll love about LearnDash is the one-click WordPress install. It makes the initial setup much a breeze. With LearnDash installed, you can quickly turn your WordPress website into a branded learning portal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason many users have fallen in love with LearnDash is that it gives greater levels of control than other learning management systems (LMS). You can easily define rules that determine who gets access to your courses and for how long. Other features include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Drip-feed course content</li><li>Set up automated permission levels to content</li><li>Award badges and certificates for significant milestones</li><li>Integration with other popular membership platforms</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If online courses are your primary line of business, then LearnDash should definitely be one of the tools on your radar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How much will LearnDash cost you?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing plans for LearnDash start at $159/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/amember/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">aMember Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Technically, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/amember/\">aMember Pro</a> was created as a PHP script you can install on your server. However, there&#8217;s an official plugin that makes integration with WordPress super easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/amember/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"304\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-aMember.png\" alt=\"Another excellent membership plugin for WordPress is aMember.\" class=\"wp-image-65143\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-aMember.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-aMember-300x130.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-aMember-600x261.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>aMember comes with unlimited membership levels and over 200 payment options (including PayPal, Stripe, and Authorize.net). It also boasts full-featured membership management, and a whole lot more. These are just some of the goodies that make it one of the best membership plugins for WordPress. Other features you can expect include, among others:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Free installation</li><li>Lots integrations</li><li>Integrated helpdesk to make customer service easier</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike other subscription-based plugins, aMember only offers a once-off lifetime license that starts at $149.36.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/s2member/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">S2 Member</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for the best free membership plugin for WordPress, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/s2member/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">S2 Member</a> is a great one.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/s2member/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-s2Member.png\" alt=\"S2 Member is another plugin that fits the best membership plugin for WordPress. \" class=\"wp-image-65149\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-s2Member.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-s2Member-300x150.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-s2Member-600x301.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Interested in testing the waters of building membership sites?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then the free version of S2Member is a great place to start. After that, however, you&#8217;ll have to upgrade to the pro version to unlock more features. These are features such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Easy to set up recurring payments</li><li>Unlimited membership levels for free memberships or paid plans</li><li>Payment gateway integrations that include Stripe, ClickBank, PayPal Pro, and Authorize.net&nbsp;</li><li>Coupon and gift codes (including coupon code tracking)</li><li>Customizable email templates</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>S2 is one of the most comprehensive membership plugins on the market despite being the cheapest. The base plan will set you back a one-time fee of $89, granting you lifetime access to all future updates.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://membermouse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MemberMouse</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating membership sites can be a challenge. <a href=\"https://membermouse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">MemberMouse</a> was created to take the grunt work out of the process.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://membermouse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"294\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-MemberMouse.png\" alt=\"MemberMouse is another excellent membership plugin for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-65150\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-MemberMouse.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-MemberMouse-300x126.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-membership-plugin-wordpress-MemberMouse-600x252.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>No matter your level of tech-savviness, you&#8217;ll find this plugin easy to use. That&#8217;s one reason it made it on our list of the best membership plugins for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>MemberMouse lets you create different membership levels and bundles. This feature makes it easy for new and existing members to purchase one-off items. You can also create trial offers and coupons to help boost conversion rates. Other notable features to expect include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Integration with various payment gateways</li><li>Integration with ESPs for email marketing</li><li>Smart tags for personalization</li><li>Optimization tools (including A/B testing)</li><li>Member management</li><li>Automated member engagement</li><li>Automatic downsells</li><li>Prorated upgrades</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to features, MemberMouse is probably top of the class. But pricing starts at $24.08/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Choosing the Best Membership Plugin for WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you&#8217;ve seen our top seven membership plugins for WordPress, you&#8217;re probably wondering which one is best for you. Here are our best of the best recommendations:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>The best overall</strong>: MemberPress</li><li><strong> Best  membership plugin for e-commerce stores</strong>: WooCommerce Membership</li><li><strong>Best membership plugin for online courses</strong>: LearnDash</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One thing you must do is take a close look at the features of each plugin and see if they align with what you want to achieve. Then, for those that offer free trials, don&#8217;t hesitate to take them for a spin to gauge their ease of use and performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Membership Plugin for WordPress — Time to Build Your Membership Site&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As you build your membership site, don&#8217;t forget that marketing is one of the keys to growth and success. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-hacks-to-grow-your-traffic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Getting noticed online</a> doesn&#8217;t happen by chance. You have to be proactive and strategic in making it happen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best ways is to have a solid SEO game plan and the tools to go with it. That&#8217;s why you must <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">download the AIOSEO plugin</a> to help ensure that your membership site and content are optimized for both search engines and users. </p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-membership-plugin-for-wordpress/\">The Best Membership Plugin for WordPress (Top 7 Compared)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://aioseo.com/best-membership-plugin-for-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attri